[{"c":"<p>Master, speak! thy servant heareth,</p><p>waiting for thy gracious word,</p><p>longing for thy voice that cheereth,</p><p>Master, let it now be heard.</p><p>I am list'ning, Lord, for thee;</p><p>what hast thou to say to me?</p>"},{"c":"<p>Speak to me by name, O Master,</p><p>let me know it is to me;</p><p>speak, that I may follow faster,</p><p>with a step more firm and free,</p><p>where the Shepherd leads the flock,</p><p>in the shadow of the Rock!</p>"},{"c":"<p>Master, speak! tho' least and lowest,</p><p>let me not unheard depart;</p><p>Master, speak! for oh, thou knowest</p><p>all the yearning of my heart,</p><p>knowest all its truest need;</p><p>speak! and make me blest indeed.</p>"},{"c":"<p>Master, speak! and make me ready,</p><p>when thy voice is truly heard,</p><p>with obedience glad and steady,</p><p>still to follow ev'ry word.</p><p>I am listening, Lord, for thee:</p><p>Master, speak, oh speak to me!</p>"}]